sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant J as Judge browser
  participant API as Express API
  participant G as gradeController
  participant DB as Supabase
  participant Au as audit_logs
  participant E as eventBus

  Note over J: Auto-save loop (debounced)
  J->>API: PUT /api/grades/:id/draft { scores, feedback }
  API->>API: protect (JWT) · gradeLimiter · zod validate
  API->>G: saveDraft
  G->>DB: SELECT existing status
  alt existing.status='submitted'
    G-->>J: 403 locked
  else
    G->>DB: UPSERT grades { status='in_progress' }
    G-->>J: 200 grade
  end

  Note over J: Final submit
  J->>API: POST /api/grades/:id/submit { scores, feedback }
  API->>G: submitGrade
  G->>DB: SELECT existing
  G->>DB: UPSERT grades { status='submitted', submitted_at }
  G-)Au: INSERT audit_logs { action='grade.submit' }
  G-)E: broadcast 'grade.submit'
  G-->>J: 200 grade
